#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:120
msgid "Loading schedule settings…"
msgstr "Läser in schemainställningar…"

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:124
msgid "WP Cron"
msgstr "WP Cron"

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:124
msgid ""
"Registers an automatic scan in WordPress at the chosen time. This schedules "
"the scan — it does not run until something executes scheduled WP events."
msgstr ""
"Registrerar en automatisk skanning i WordPress vid vald tid. Detta "
"schemalägger skanningen — den körs inte förrän något kör schemalagda "
"WP-händelser."

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:132
msgid "Automatic scan"
msgstr "Automatisk skanning"

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:132
msgid "Schedule a recurring scan via WordPress cron."
msgstr "Schemalägg en återkommande skanning via WordPress cron."

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:139
msgid "Scan frequency"
msgstr "Skanningsfrekvens"

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:139
msgid "Daily"
msgstr "Daglig"

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:139
msgid "Weekly"
msgstr "Veckovis"

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:139
msgid "How often the scheduled scan is registered."
msgstr "Hur ofta den schemalagda skanningen registreras."

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:146
msgid "Scan time"
msgstr "Skanningstid"

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:154
msgid "Time of day to register the scan (server time)."
msgstr "Tid på dagen då skanningen registreras (servertid)."

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:161
msgid "Batch size"
msgstr "Batchstorlek"

#: resources/assets/js/schedule/ScheduleTab.tsx:170
msgid ""
"Pages processed per background tick. Larger values finish scheduled scans "
"faster but use more memory."
msgstr ""
"Sidor som bearbetas per bakgrundstick. Större värden ger snabbare "
"schemalagda skanningar men mer minne."

